defaultUKCTA is a trade association promoting the interests of competitive fixed-line telecommunications companies competing against BT, as well as each other, in the residential and business markets. Its role is to develop and promote the interests of its member
defaults to Ofcom and the Government. Details of membership of UKCTA can be found at 
