defaultThere is a considerable body of consumer protection law already whic
defaulth UKCTA believes adequately protects consumers today. Communications Providers are regulated sector specific regulations and in particular General Condition 9 of the General Conditions of Entitlement regime monitored by Ofcom. This condition sets out certa
defaultin mandatory provisions which must be included in consumer contracts. 
