defaultAlthough the Government has reasoned that clarification to consumer rights is important because ‘consumers are more lik
defaultely to suffer detriment they are unable to resolve’, for the communications industry that is simply not the case. As part of the General Conditions of Entitlement regime all communications providers are required to be part of an ADR scheme; 
defaultthese arrangeme
defaultnts are widely regarded as effective and the ADR schemes are well utilised by consumers. 
default&#xa0;
defaultWe consider that this additional layer of consumer protection 
defaultis unnecessary and disproportionate. 
